Title : Comedy Playhouse (series 16)
Text : {{citation style|date=May 2014}}

The '''sixteenth  series''' of '''''[[Comedy Playhouse]]''''', the long-running [[BBC]] series, aired during 2014, with only three episodes.

==Background==
The sixteenth series, consisted of three episodes, each of which had a different cast and storyline. It was announced that ''Miller's Mountain'' was going to be made into a series, whereas ''Monks'' was not. No decision was announced regarding ''Over to Bill''. 

''Miller's Mountain'' was renamed ''[[Mountain Goats (BBC series)|Mountain Goats]]'' and a six-part series aired on BBC One from 14 August 2015.<ref>https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b066gfc7</ref> The series received overwhelmingly negative reviews.<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2015/aug/15/mountain-goats-review-who-are-these-people-anyway-laugh-at-anything | work = The Guardian | title = Mountain Goats review – ‘Who are these people, who’ll laugh at anything?’ | accessdate=25 November 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2015/aug/14/ripper-street-rick-stein-venice-istanbul | work = The Guardian | title = Friday's best TV | accessdate=25 November 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/millers-mountain-comedy-playhouse-bbc-tv-review-unfortunately-the-return-of-comedy-playhouse-is-no-9328222.html | work = Independent | title = Miller's Mountain, Comedy Playhouse - BBC, TV review: The return of Comedy Playhouse is no laughing matter | accessdate=25 November 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.thecustardtv.com/2015/08/matt-on-box-new-tricks-who-do-you-think.html | title = Matt on the Box: New Tricks, Who Do You Think You Are, Mountain Goats and Young Free and Single | work = The Custard TV | accessdate=25 November 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://uktvreviewer.wordpress.com/2015/08/16/mountain-goats-bbc1-review/ | work = UK TV Reviewer | title = Mountain Goats (BBC1) Review | accessdate=25 November 2016}}</ref>

