|[[Doug Naylor]]
|29 April 2014
|30 mins
|When BBC weatherman Bill Onion ([[Hugh Dennis]]) is fired in a departmental shake-up, a blackly farcical train of events begins which ends in his humiliation in front of a prospective employer from another network. Also starring [[Neil Morrissey]] as Jez.
